## Performance Considerations

**Bundle Size:**
- **Konva:** ~50KB gzipped
- **Our diagram code:** ~30-40KB (estimated)
- **Total:** ~80-90KB for entire diagram feature
- **Lazy-loaded:** No initial bundle impact
- **Still under 100KB target**

**Runtime Performance:**
- Konva is highly optimized (canvas-based)
- Scales to 1000+ elements smoothly
- Hardware accelerated
- Debounced auto-save (2s)
- IndexedDB persistence (non-blocking)

**Export Performance:**
- PNG: Konva toDataURL (~50-100ms)
- SVG: Custom serialization (~100ms)
- PDF: jsPDF generation (~200ms)

